{"tid":1768353,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「盲撐」以後唔准再屌黃店難食","createTime":"2019-12-04T04:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T17:01:07.000Z","uid":13361,"like":21,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8191015e9d5d1cdf15bb6818f6a1f7d835fe35ed","tid":1768353,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"大家同路人 有咩唔岩咪不完美 可接受 要改善<br />\n就算你唔敢當面同佢講返 都可以fb/ig去提出改善建議 例如太咸 太貴之類 <br />\n咩野食過一次無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對家從來都唔割蓆 我地都唔可以拋棄任何一位手足 有咩做得唔好 你唔講人地未必知 <br />\n希望大家依家即刻pm返你覺得有問題嘅黃店 就算無問題 都可以比下建議有咩可以做得更好 例如服務 環境 衛生之類 如果比左建議 下次無改善 先再blacklist 好唔好？"},{"pid":"388d93c6e5d756f7c81158b8be2b3b1e9fd1e621","tid":1768353,"uid":156509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"正名翻，唔係「盲撐」，而係不完美 可接受 要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe2754074037f6cc890849f3547aa3b13b5a672","tid":1768353,"uid":2950,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"388d93c6e5d756f7c81158b8be2b3b1e9fd1e621","tid":1768353,"uid":156509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"正名翻，唔係「盲撐」，而係不完美 可接受 要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"好撚心唔好跟黑警用埋啲垃圾句"},{"pid":"95eaf1ea939b989b7f6897a7b6b6712fc6cc95f5","tid":1768353,"uid":71508,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n黃店永遠都係最好食<br />\n就算唔好食都要照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349fd2d930e87a106b9743ea7efc557584945231","tid":1768353,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe2754074037f6cc890849f3547aa3b13b5a672","tid":1768353,"uid":2950,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"388d93c6e5d756f7c81158b8be2b3b1e9fd1e621","tid":1768353,"uid":156509,"like